r />\n耶穌親身示範"},{"pid":"a06ad3cb74b4433e19e2ad5a8240151680670bd5","tid":1199743,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wnna7js.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnna7js.gif&h=bb3b70c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d00ba14268745003e9b1b24aef7dbf56fb952e9a","tid":1199743,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"好多人分唔到天主教同基督教<br />\n簡單D，天主教以前好惡又望開真道，一班人頂唔順就出左黎成立新教，中間又比唔同政府同教派打擊，一路打到今日既基督教。<br />\n所以基督教可以話係抗爭既老祖宗。"},{"pid":"b428fa2ef33f0e50d8fcff2d1d918f1a09f3944f","tid":1199743,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大量和理非一齊唱聖詩<br />\n好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想去支持佢地"},{"pid":"ab85c0329881e13f6e06ce70009bca66be177a99","tid":1199743,"uid":12360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"唱歌黎講耶撚係屈機過左膠好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但耶撚勁在大把歌唱 可以提升士氣"},{"pid":"31362171a73571b2bc1b1849b2e60a64ad916d6a","tid":1199743,"uid":12565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"22afadc5752f9e78aa2a8f70319bd6877574d481","tid":1199743,"uid":26106,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"今次就撐耶撚啦<br />\n好過咩都唔做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"人數好撚緊要<br />\n就算唔認同勇武<br />\n和理非都要出嚟陪坐<br />\n齋坐又好唱歌又好祈禱又好<br />\n唔好孤立勇武<br />\n有乜事兩邊先可以互相照應互通消息"}]}